{"tid":1595531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制藍色商戶，由生活細節做起","createTime":"2019-09-26T06:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T15:28:30.000Z","uid":31405,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7069dadc76a647466bb067b718f99bd714629b0c","tid":1595531,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"我都明有時要改變個生活習慣同食野既地方<br />\n一時三刻係好難適應<br />\n但當大家諗下前線既義士，被捕既手足既下場同被虐待既經歷<br />\n再加埋d仆街藍色商戶既難聽說話同每一句既拉得好，打得好，就會有動力去抵制班冚家剷<br />\n<br />\n最近我都專登去左搵黃色既舖頭食野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWYXZoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWYXZoO.jpg&h=f1758c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTkrSJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTkrSJU.jpg&h=6c5bf493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家都做得到！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"1cb2d8f02a4aeee958cde8a7e6f29f01f33e2d42","tid":1595531,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"Push推 support<br />\nSignature簽名檔：保衛家園，對抗極權<br />\n條例撒回了，但問題根源還在<br />\n反送中運動轉型為「反極權運動」<br />\n守護香港呢個家，尋求深層次改革<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">行動：Connect 新疆/台灣/中共受害者<br />\n大搞文宣，主線：反極權，撐民主自由<br />\n通過人權與民主法案前，減少暴力畫面<br />\n減輕國際戰線壓力，求加辣/高票數通過<br />\n將「自由對抗極權」傳到世界各地</span><br />\n#antitotalitarianism #anti-chinazi <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>麻煩手足暫時停止升級武力(鏡頭前<br />\n文宣/輿論需要時間追上（國際戰線要人<br />\n(抗爭需要轉型,可持續發展)<br />\n要更多機會比和理非參與<br />\n達至全民一齊追求普世價值</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n衛城革命,生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡,打倒腐敗<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值/level</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能6.低消費、高儲蓄<br />\n<strong><em>每日任務：</em></strong>1.幫襯良心商店、抵制送中商戶2.開AC玩國際戰線 (Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)3.多發佈正面資訊、冷處理負面POST4.十點咆哮發泄5.思考完就take action<br />\n<strong><em>每星期任務</em></strong>：1. 罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手4.參加一樣民主活動5. 諗下點樣爭取民主<br />\n<strong><em>每月任務</em></strong>：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=b8f0a7df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=ee9d7fc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c0af0e60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.26<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">極權如何打壓香港示威？<br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨<br />\n2.誤導：送中條例、說謊、黃色object等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n諗到再加</span>"},{"pid":"8ebab1a4fe1a8c4b97869f445965ca83eca117ba","tid":1595531,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T06:40:37.000Z","msg":"（有圖）各師兄弟 歸位未？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595382</a>"},{"pid":"e09655aa9ddf0de7b7e9c5e00ae3f2fe4b0b2ba9","tid":1595531,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84083bca10b7bb9c5f508ff56e6d67852ca4bff1","tid":1595531,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"試多咗新嘢"},{"pid":"55829a8d091eb056a8ef9f09dd3018baa7efcd9e","tid":1595531,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee9d1bc23ab9bec61098aa40393c4ce5534a84b9","tid":1595531,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"你班友響應左未呀？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785fdc70857f399047e20cda64bee214e9f84936","tid":1595531,"uid":181180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"星期五日byebuyday<br />\n改食小店 你我有責<br />\n <br />\n明日愛丁堡支援新屋嶺義士集會"},{"pid":"94c2be28319ba1bad1c5d717489fad1a5405f058","tid":1595531,"uid":197846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"反正跳閘 黃色小店幾遠都要去懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}